{"tid":1497103,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[屌你老母牆頭草] 朋友又係警察又去發夢係咩玩法","createTime":"2019-08-22T22:22:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-23T02:59:48.000Z","uid":201529,"like":9,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"4e4efee3efb1c5139798ae52d277e312aa39f84c","tid":1497103,"uid":201529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T22:22:36.000Z","msg":"天下警察一樣黑<br />\n你一日唔辭職<br />\n一日都要聽order做嘢<br />\n一日都係選擇性執法<br />\n唔好同我講你起前線發夢做左幾多嘢<br />\n呢啲只係你贖罪嘅方法<br />\n唔好講到好忍辱負重咁<br />\n<br />\n當然我唔排除你係牆頭草<br />\n因為你身邊朋友同事藍黃都有<br />\n對住藍絲講你係黑警<br />\n對住黃絲講你有發夢<br />\n兩邊朋友都唔會得失<br />\n人工照𢭃<br />\n重有印象分加<br />\n<br />\n食晒兩家茶飯<br />\n真係好嘔心"},{"pid":"e9f4ca5f418384e4032f26e45fee105302ceaaf6","tid":1497103,"uid":64345,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T22:23:24.000Z","msg":"喬裝成唔同既人物"},{"pid":"7c8e7ce813389f60918777a075f7227be376e249","tid":1497103,"uid":201529,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T22:25:17.000Z","msg":"我唔想當面屌7你<br />\n希望你睇到個post<br />\n我唔介意你藍<br />\n但牆頭草真係好嘔心"},{"pid":"e3ae9d7790d4b3e87335c360c729a551faf7ba8f","tid":1497103,"uid":161462,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"7c8e7ce813389f60918777a075f7227be376e249","tid":1497103,"uid":201529,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T22:25:17.000Z","msg":"我唔想當面屌7你<br />\n希望你睇到個post<br />\n我唔介意你藍<br />\n但牆頭草真係好嘔心"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T22:30:50.000Z","msg":"有人係入邊咪可以報夢囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09f87f828c302f1d51a1a29825fcac0001a8afd8","tid":1497103,"uid":201529,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e3ae9d7790d4b3e87335c360c729a551faf7ba8f","tid":1497103,"uid":161462,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"7c8e7ce813389f60918777a075f7227be376e249","tid":1497103,"uid":201529,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T22:25:17.000Z","ms